channel.description:
[URL=http://img5.imageshack.us/i/bannersh.png/][IMG]http://img5.imageshack.us/img5/4907/bannersh.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img5/bannersh.png/1/][IMG]http://img5.imageshack.us/img5/bannersh.png/1/w600.png[/img][/URL]
[URL=http://img4.imageshack.us/i/specdemo.gif/][IMG]http://img4.imageshack.us/img4/9237/specdemo.gif[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img4/specdemo.gif/1/][IMG]http://img4.imageshack.us/img4/specdemo.gif/1/w348.png[/img][/URL] alright, yo i guess, my names ginugon or glestrts, depends which forums. lol, I am both an avid private server person and runescape member... go figure...lol
I currently have a project set out for the next few weeks / months. I do not have internet access so [u]I am not[/u] planning on hosting this. But i will release.
Update: I have scratched the idea of textural reworking and redoing the sprites, i just played a 508 and the textures were phenomenal, so i feel that the people who want graphics will want 503+
Also this is key: This is my first client, and also, my second source, first was a delta...
Server: Final devolution 2.7 credits to killamess.
done:
Removed all skills, cleaned the source added over 100 lines of npc dialogue, 3 new skill interfaces, a new skill, a new prayer handler for the prayers (eagle eye, mystic might, etc)
To Do. Make a non delta pvp, with [u]no overpowered weapons or armors,[/u] zthis means no godswords, bandos, or pvp gear fellows, but i will include the data for the specs and item stats comments within the source.
[size=20pt]Dharok will once again be the most destructive armor in Runescape![/size]
Client: Base: 317 deob, i literally watched a tutorial on youtube and extracted this from the cache.
[size=30pt]Updates (weekly)[/size] [size=20pt]PvP Drops! [URL=http://img4.imageshack.us/i/javs2.gif/][IMG]http://img4.imageshack.us/img4/6598/javs2.gif[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img4/javs2.gif/1/][IMG]http://img4.imageshack.us/img4/javs2.gif/1/w399.png[/img][/URL]

[size=20pt]Old Updates:[/size]
[b]Added Level up Message!!!![/b] [URL=http://img683.imageshack.us/i/levelup.png/][IMG]http://img683.imageshack.us/img683/7200/levelup.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img683/levelup.png/1/][IMG]http://img683.imageshack.us/img683/levelup.png/1/w518.png[/img][/URL] [b] Hardcoded pray interface,[/b] need to work on hovering, also replacing my sprites with the 317 versions cause they look awe full. Aweso need to fix deactivation of the range and mage prayers [URL=http://img4.imageshack.us/i/newprayers.png/][IMG]http://img4.imageshack.us/img4/5832/newprayers.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img4/newprayers.png/1/][IMG]http://img4.imageshack.us/img4/newprayers.png/1/w240.png[/img][/URL]

[b]Prayer Interface--- WIP[/b], need to add the new prayers for range and mage, and also pray icons. [URL=http://img4.imageshack.us/i/prayerinterface.png/][IMG]http://img4.imageshack.us/img4/268/prayerinterface.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img4/prayerinterface.png/1/][IMG]http://img4.imageshack.us/img4/prayerinterface.png/1/w511.png[/img][/URL]
[size=20pt]Creditz[/size]
The Makers of Runescape Me Demise Pking for the cache Mitko- for his class 9 which was a great teaching tool because of the interfaces, however i have not used his code Coonhunter- for hp bars tut, although i just used it to find the right method.
[size=20pt][u][b]Junk from textural reworking[/b][/u][/size] [code]
[size=30pt]I overwrote the client, tell me which things to re add and which to delete[/size] [size=20pt]I was using totalcommander as my rar unpacker cause i was too lazy to dl winrar. Downlaoded saluspking or something and it extracted overtop my client, the latest backup i have is a fail, so i am starting with another 317 deob, this time i will keep the 317 gameframe (mostly) and all that will be replaced are the sprites.
Client is back at 0, in terms of clicking areas, and other stuff, Interfaces and stuff are all archived aswell as the javs, so thats not bad, orbs are gone, and i really dont care [/size]
[size=20pt]Most recent Hardcoded Update:[/size] Hard coding ancients interface WiP
Earth strike is teles, and weaken is miasmic,
[URL=http://img8.imageshack.us/i/ancientsinterface.png/][IMG]http://img8.imageshack.us/img8/9885/ancientsinterface.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img8/ancientsinterface.png/1/][IMG]http://img8.imageshack.us/img8/ancientsinterface.png/1/w769.png[/img][/URL]
Also you can see my custom hp bars and gameframe,
[b] Hardcoded Teleport Interface[/b]--- [URL=http://img21.imageshack.us/i/teleporttab.png/][IMG]http://img21.imageshack.us/img21/1830/teleporttab.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img21/teleporttab.png/1/][IMG]http://img21.imageshack.us/img21/teleporttab.png/1/w240.png[/img][/URL]
Note: I am scratching the teleport interface because i am working on sorting the normal f2p spellbook.
[s]I plan on making a worldwide dueling server, but with challenging in edgeville, cause personally i think al karid based servers are fail. I also am looking for a good duel base, so i can edit it and make worlwide dueling, based upon moving the players a certain distance from each other, but ill need to wwrite a few ints based on player position.[/s]
I plan on making a non delta based PVP source. Proof of this: [URL=http://img27.imageshack.us/i/proofoffinaldevo.png/][IMG]http://img27.imageshack.us/img27/9156/proofoffinaldevo.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img27/proofoffinaldevo.png/1/][IMG]http://img27.imageshack.us/img27/proofoffinaldevo.png/1/w769.png[/img][/URL]
failed miasmic spell (redoing the whole thing) it looks like shit

This is my client I currently am working on a 317 Ed (extreme detail, original right?), my current project is to rework the [b][u]entire[/u][/b] amount of sprites and textures, so far i have (click thecodebox)
Why ED???? well thats the difference between you and me, if i called it hd, people would be like "OMG @@@ wth dude thats not real hd"
and also they are custom textures, that i pixeled with microsoft paint, i used to be into banners and sigs when i did rs.
so i basically compromised and made a whole new name.
This is meh 317 ED client, eat your hearts out. I have now added 508 char models, creditz to demises cache
